                            similique? Cupiditate exercitationem eum expedita laborum nobis nesciunt voluptates hic
                            cumque? Fugit vel quos ducimus quae labore saepe.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col s12 m6">
                    <div class="icon-block">
                        <h2 class="center brown-text"><i class="material-icons">translate</i></h2>
                        <h5 class="center">Multi-lingual</h5>

                        <p class="light">Lorem ipsum dolor sit, amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Omnis necessitatibus
                            maiores corporis, minus veritatis alias ab expedita eveniet dolore, perspiciatis recusandae
                            ipsam! Corporis tempora qui dolorem velit excepturi illum ab.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col s12 m6">
                    <div class="icon-block">
                        <h2 class="center brown-text"><i class="material-icons">graphic_eq</i></h2>
                        <h5 class="center">Text to Speech</h5>

                        <p class="light">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur, adipisicing elit. Commodi doloremque
                            cupiditate dicta, illum at, officiis esse a magnam voluptates nesciunt nostrum, recusandae
                            deserunt voluptatibus harum debitis soluta itaque odio tempora.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col s12 m6">
                    <div class="icon-block">
                        <h2 class="center brown-text"><i class="material-icons">3d_rotation</i></h2>
                        <h5 class="center">Augmented Reality</h5>

                        <p class="light">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur, adipisicing elit. Labore alias saepe
                            voluptate ipsum commodi eos enim nobis ullam! Maxime minus pariatur ut corporis nemo. Hic
                            repellat sint corporis at fugiat!</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>


    <div class="parallax-container valign-wrapper">
        <div class="section no-pad-bot">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row center">
                    <h5 class="header col s12 light">Lorem, ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit.

                    </h5>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="parallax"><img src="img/taj_mahal.jpg" alt="Unsplashed background img 2"></div>
    </div>



    <div class="container" id="monument-search-section">
        <div class="section">

            <div class="container">
                <div class="center">
                    <h4>Where do you want to visit?</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <form class="col s12  center" action="/tts" method="POST">
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="input-field col s12">
                                <!-- <i class="material-icons prefix">tour</i> -->
                                <input name="monument" type="text" id="monument-name" required />
                                <label for="monument-name">Monument</label>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="input-field col s12 m12">
                                <!-- <i class="material-icons prefix">translate</i> -->
                                <select name="languages" id="language" class="icons" required>
                                    <option value="" disabled selected>Select Language</option>
                                    <% langs.map((language) => { %>
                                    <option value="<%= language[1][0] %>"><%= language[0] %></option>
                                    <% })%>

                                </select>
                                <label>Languages</label>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <button class="btn waves-effect waves-light" type="submit" name="action">Submit
                            <i class="material-icons right">send</i>
                        </button>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>




    <div class="parallax-container valign-wrapper">
        <div class="section no-pad-bot">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row center">
                    <h5 class="header col s12 light">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit.
                    </h5>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="parallax"><img src="img/christ.jpg" alt="Unsplashed background img 3"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="container" id="ar-model-section">
        <div class="section">

            <div class="container">
                <div class="center">
                    <h4>Bring monuments to life</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <form class="col s12  center" action="/arModel" method="POST">
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="input-field col s12">
                                <!-- <i class="material-icons prefix">tour</i> -->
                                <input name="monument_ar" type="text" id="monument-name-ar" required />
                                <label for="monument-name-ar">Monument</label>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <button class="btn waves-effect waves-light" type="submit" name="action">AR
                            Model
                            <i class="material-icons right">send</i>
                        </button>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="page-footer teal">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col l6 s12">
                    <h5 class="white-text">Company Bio</h5>
                    <p class="grey-text text-lighten-4">We are a team of college students working on this project like
                        it's our
                        full time job. Any amount would help support and continue development on this project and is
                        greatly
                        appreciated.</p>


                </div>
                <div class="col l3 s12">
                    <h5 class="white-text">Settings</h5>
                    <ul>
                        <li><a class="white-text" href="#!">Link 1</a></li>
                        <li><a class="white-text" href="#!">Link 2</a></li>
                        <li><a class="white-text" href="#!">Link 3</a></li>
                        <li><a class="white-text" href="#!">Link 4</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="col l3 s12">
                    <h5 class="white-text">Connect</h5>
                    <ul>
                        <li><a class="white-text" href="#!">Link 1</a></li>
                        <li><a class="white-text" href="#!">Link 2</a></li>
                        <li><a class="white-text" href="#!">Link 3</a></li>
                        <li><a class="white-text" href="#!">Link 4</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
